"title": "8638: benedictions",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8638: benedictions",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Prayers invoking God's blessing upon others. They are often spoken at a time of impending separation, although they may sometimes constitute greetings.</p>\n<h2>Benedictions pronounced by priests</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:23-Num6:27\">NUM 6:23–6:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:5\">DEU 21:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:20\">1SA 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:27\">2CH 30:27</a></p>\n<h2>Benedictions pronounced by kings</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:54-1Kgs8:61\">1KI 8:54–8:61</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:18-Gen14:20\">GEN 14:18–14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:20\">2SA 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:3-2Chr6:11\">2CH 6:3–6:11</a></p>\n<h2>Benedictions pronounced by other leaders of the nation of Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:6-Josh22:8\">JOS 22:6–22:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:1-Deut33:29\">DEU 33:1–33:29</a></p>\n<h2>Benedictions pronounced by family members</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:8-Ruth1:9\">RUT 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:60\">GEN 24:60</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:27-Gen27:29\">GEN 27:27–27:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:9-Gen48:22\">GEN 48:9–48:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:1-Gen49:28\">GEN 49:1–49:28</a></p>\n<h2>Apostolic benedictions on the church</h2>\n<h3>The blessing of grace and peace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:7\">ROM 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:20\">ROM 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:3\">1CO 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:23\">1CO 16:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:2-Gal1:5\">GAL 1:2–1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:16\">GAL 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:2\">EPH 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:23\">EPH 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:2\">1TI 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:21\">REV 22:21</a></p>\n<h3>The blessing of spiritual growth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">HEB 13:20–13:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>The blessing of God in all his fulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:14\">2CO 13:14</a></strong></p>",
